@Regrann from @northcentralshelter - Valentine’s Day is just around the corner and Bonni is still hoping to find her sweetheart! This gorgeous, well-mannered gal is ready to go home today with a lucky family! 💘
Bonni is extremely sweet, walks well on the leash, and loves to play with tennis balls in the yard with volunteers. She also fancies herself a lady of leisure and loves to hop up on the chair and sit next to you. 😁 At 6 years of age, she is the perfect mix of a playful dog and couch potato, and is sure to be a loyal companion!
Bonni is ready to find a forever home complete with a couch & humans to love! She has been at the shelter since September 2017 and weighs 65 pounds.
